     1	# AreaMatrix Validation Report Format
     2	
     3	Use this structure when reporting validation choices or results.
     4	
     5	## Format
     6	
     7	```text
     8	改动范围:
     9	- <paths or task labels>
    10	
    11	改了什么:
    12	- <core behavior, docs, rules, or generated materials changed>
    13	
    14	为什么这样改:
    15	- <task/docs/governance/risk boundary that required the change>
    16	
    17	推荐验证:
    18	- <commands and why they are sufficient>
    19	
    20	已运行:
    21	- <command>: <fresh result, exit status, key evidence>
    22	
    23	未运行:
    24	- <command>: <reason>
    25	
    26	证据新鲜度:
    27	- <which results were rerun after the final relevant change>
    28	
    29	工程质量:
    30	- <coding standards, comments, error handling, tests, and maintainability evidence>
    31	
    32	Blocker:
    33	- Review: clear / blocked / not-applicable
    34	- Security: clear / blocked / not-applicable
    35	- Dependency: clear / blocked / not-applicable
    36	- CI: clear / blocked / not-applicable
    37	- Git evidence: clear / blocked / not-applicable
    38	
    39	结果:
    40	- PASS / FAIL / BLOCKED / NOT-READY
    41	
    42	残余风险:
    43	- <remaining risk or None>
    44	```
    45	
    46	## Rules
    47	
    48	- `已运行` means the command actually ran in this workspace.
    49	- `证据新鲜度` must say whether the command ran after the final relevant file change; stale output cannot support a completion claim.
    50	- `未运行` must include a concrete reason, not a vague note.
    51	- `PASS` requires all required checks to pass or be explicitly out of scope.
    52	- `PASS` also requires the implementation to satisfy `engineering-quality-rules.md` and `docs/development/coding-standards.md`.
    53	- `PASS` is invalid when review, security, dependency, CI, or Git evidence blockers remain; use `BLOCKED` or `NOT-READY`.
    54	- `BLOCKED` is correct when the environment cannot run a required check.
    55	- `NOT-READY` is correct when work remains even though some validation commands passed.
    56	- Dry-run can validate runner wiring, but never validates product implementation.
    57	- Old logs, prior memories, screenshots, mock-only paths, fixture-only paths, hardcoded success, and agent self-reports are not completion evidence.
    58	
    59	## Common Phrases
    60	
    61	Use:
    62	
    63	- `未运行: 当前环境缺少 X，无法执行 Y。`
    64	- `残余风险: 未覆盖 macOS 真机交互，仅完成 build/test。`
    65	- `结果: BLOCKED，原因是必需验证命令无法在当前环境完成。`
    66	
    67	Avoid:
    68	
    69	- `应该没问题`
    70	- `看起来通过`
    71	- `dry-run 已证明 task 完成`

